---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Writing | Shiqing Gao"
  description="Learning notes, project reflections, and language or expression experiments by Shiqing Gao."
>
  <header class="container page-header personal-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Writing / 文字</p>
    <h1>记录理解一个问题的过程。</h1>
    <p>这里会放一些学习记录、项目复盘、表达练习和零散想法。相比“成品展示”，这里更关注我如何理解一个问题、如何整理一个项目，以及一些语言和表达上的尝试。</p>
  </header>

  <section class="container writing-empty section">
    <div class="writing-index" aria-hidden="true">W—01</div>
    <div>
      <h2>内容会慢慢补上。</h2>
      <p>未来这里会包括图像反问题项目复盘、学习笔记和一些中英表达练习。文章只会在真正写完并适合公开时出现。</p>
      <p class="english-note">This is a place for working notes and reflections, not a feed that needs to be filled on schedule.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
